title: You’ve Unlocked a New Gift
headline: You’ve Unlocked a New Gift
subtitle: Safari Ranger Överflöd Entity MT Livery
content:
Thank you for completing 3 First Dose missions on Hard difficulty between January 12 and February 8. Your gift of the Safari Ranger Överflöd Entity MT Livery will be available before February 17.

Stay tuned to the Rockstar Newswire for more limited-time events coming soon.
